{"tid":2138520,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［人血鬼］會員「下亞厘畢道」兜售口罩呃錢，被要求退錢後公開客戶個人資料！","createTime":"2020-08-03T15:38:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T03:32:54.000Z","uid":219007,"like":46,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"005b9c78dd650eb26cbe90823051989783e6fab7","tid":2138520,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T15:38:48.000Z","msg":"會員「下亞厘畢道」好人好者竟然指黃世澤係BNO平權最大推手，並每分每刻都在追擊黃毓民是「人血九大鬼」PR<br />\n<br />\n仲話黃世澤（其實係自己）有引用自己文章<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BqLgFJn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBqLgFJn.png&h=be691fa6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n會員「下亞厘畢道」黃世柒賣口罩呃錢，大批苦主追討賠款，下亞厘畢道（世柒）幾時捨得還錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL9A8uTK.jpg&amp;h=cc58e418&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9AJqw63.jpg&amp;h=9721e687&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaDyuekn.jpg&amp;h=235706aa&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5jFMgyF.jpg&amp;h=0c2cc56c&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRyV05rZ.jpg&amp;h=c1ff3455&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\n同黃世澤買口罩，Paypal 退錢佢會話保險公司black list你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZhVwsFi.jpg&amp;h=8f7febf7&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來因為搵左容樂其訴苦，所以要公開哂佢資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9AsZDxy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9AsZDxy.jpg&h=96d5dd0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原來真係唔知一個中招<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/czhVWkp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FczhVWkp.png&h=cfcf12df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">「下亞厘畢道」（章魚嘴），乖啦，快啲俾返啲錢人啦</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/unclepeterlee/1464648351-97068575.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Funclepeterlee%2F1464648351-97068575.jpg&h=54c9166e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3c8d08dfbe3b87c0b6582ec5e0a915f0958f8697","tid":2138520,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T15:41:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1619d9571cbdacd6732df1e083b304930514d5d1","tid":2138520,"uid":219007,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T15:45:14.000Z","msg":"幫黃世澤買野?<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1982413\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1982413</a><br />\n<br />\n#15<br />\n求Q奇<br />\n&bull;<br />\n26 日前<br />\n今日佢終於收到我個dispute, 然後就係佢個網度過我騙佢，仲公佈我資料。 我其實dispute 佢個時都預左，與其搵佢退錢， 佢都係會公佈人既資料 然後話人地唔岩， 我寧願要佢比人罰。<br />\n<br />\n我都建議大家如果中招，都用dispute, 唔好比條撚樣再借住黃色經濟圈害其他人。<br />\n<br />\n呢個對話係我比佢拖左2個月之後既對話，仲話出貨。<br />\n <img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVq3qFyb.jpg&amp;h=ec645d9a&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBCHODjR.jpg&amp;h=cfee0e9d&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n仲有，受害人真係唔少，我跟據比佢block 既list, send email 問啲受害人， 個個都係被拖 被騙 然後就被公佈資料。 我希望大家可以幫手推上啲呢個post. 起碼要佢受影響"},{"pid":"3ab85947e7ef3ab1a16b6e3d013cc5aaff11cca0","tid":2138520,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T15:48:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d912bb389ae2782ceb9df3f57d54b2f631f8af5a","tid":2138520,"uid":196968,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T15:48:37.000Z","msg":"碌左個橙入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇黎又有人食饅頭食飽鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"542e9d9f59bfc9042d1e74bc0e47db2688a56fab","tid":2138520,"uid":244082,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d912bb389ae2782ceb9df3f57d54b2f631f8af5a","tid":2138520,"uid":196968,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T15:48:37.000Z","msg":"碌左個橙入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇黎又有人食饅頭食飽鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T15:51:47.000Z","msg":"好撚飽 最少成千張單， 成球港幣！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"415833ba07c3007bb5b4384b09543951432d81cb","tid":2138520,"uid":219007,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T15:53:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rM23kTN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrM23kTN.png&h=aab7805f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong>俾返啲錢人啦下亞厘畢道</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj