bfc9042d1e74bc0e47db2688a56fab","tid":2138520,"uid":244082,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d912bb389ae2782ceb9df3f57d54b2f631f8af5a","tid":2138520,"uid":196968,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T15:48:37.000Z","msg":"碌左個橙入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇黎又有人食饅頭食飽鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T15:51:47.000Z","msg":"好撚飽 最少成千張單， 成球港幣！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T15:53:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要計歐元黎食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T15:59:42.000Z","msg":"擺定期1個月都抵啦。我唔係唔比返錢你，係我我賺左囉！"},{"pid":"b9addb5c34fef4a49bf76579e6f7b994d39318c5","tid":2138520,"uid":219007,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T16:11:54.000Z","msg":"睇吓而家暗共既八大人血鬼有邊幾個先，根據會員「下亞厘畢道」深入分析得出嘅結果，你會見到有幾條分支分部，而各分支之間貌似冇關，但其實入邊千絲萬縷：<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y9PpPSX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY9PpPSX.jpg&h=ea5e7cb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>黃世柒</strong></span>，原名章魚嘴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。因筆名與「黃洋達」同姓，因此是暗熱狗。 在武漢肺炎肆虐期間，因網上兜售口罩無貨出，不肯退錢。遭受多名苦主追討賠償，章其後不甘被追討決定公開苦主資料。 其行徑成功躋身第一大人血鬼！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic4.zhimg.com%2F50%2Fv2-50c4a722b7c8b2eca5840b12a51c6f6a_r.jpg&amp;h=3bdf3f8c&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<span class=\"violet\"><span class=\"small\"><strong>林夕</strong>，香港填詞人。因筆名「林夕」發音與特首「林鄭」極為相似，故他被質疑一早已是暗共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。於2020年八月上旬發表要求泛民辭職言論，與頭號人物黃毓民風格一致，分化民主派證據確鑿。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqtBfMDk.jpg&amp;h=5911e71b&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n毓線<br />\n<strong>黃毓民(頭號人物）</strong>，常批評香港民主派，嚴人寬己是他招牌風格。 傳說中他其中的一位兒子遭美國要脅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，於是他後期出現反中言論，令一眾親中派質疑他出賣同路人，分化親中力量<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。他經常於關鍵時刻以攻擊民主人士來分化抗爭力量，達到瓦解民主運動目的。<br />\n<br />\n佢旗下亦有唔同爪牙以作不同任務。因政治魅力強大而為KOL頭號人物，影響力深遠！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU0cyyiJ.jpg&amp;h=690d6901&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<strong>熱血公民</strong>，為黃毓民爪牙（毓線），假裝與黃毓民分裂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。他們常以黃毓民手法分化同路人，更批評香港市民戴口罩是白癡。 企圖借呢啲手法瓦解公民社會網絡，以達致摧毁民主運動目的。雙重標準亦是熱血公民露底弊病，當批評別人參選時，自己又參選，龍門任擺，最終臭名遠播。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYdLcOR9.jpg&amp;h=4761470e&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<strong>陳雲</strong>，為熱血公民羽黨，毓線下小分支，以鬼神論吸引迷信者，以達將熱血公民教會式神化。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCWFwjYX.jpg&amp;h=8a2f895c&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<strong>白兵</strong>，曾參與星戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，戰後回流地球，其後登上Myradio作客串，毓線人物。他與泛民主派一樣只係識選舉議題。佢亦有自己頻道，他主要針對議會戰線作出攻擊，破壞民主派議會戰線。 最終政府取消選舉，正合白兵本意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQCZw4qK.jpg&amp;h=1c9fbd24&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n啤線<br />\n<strong>啤梨</strong>，新冒起的政治娛樂KOL。外表俊朗，據説配合個人魅力於年青時曾迷倒不少少女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。現在扮到非常包容，但有時亦會潑抗爭者冷水，導出香港現實，目的好明顯係要令人心灰意冷移民，以達至瓦解運動。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實只要起底以前的網台節目，就會發現佢一樣經常批評民主派。 泛民衝屌，唔衝又屌，亦會喺關鍵時候為黃毓民辯護。該網台入邊亦有客串主持包括沈四海等國民黨藍營背景人士，與香港親中顏色「藍」不謀而合，他亦與黃毓民友好，證明啤梨台與黃毓民關係密切。 現時啤梨擁護者非常多，每晚節目現場即時有一萬觀眾觀看，其影響力不容忽視，大眾必需對他加倍注視！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FywCKEZa.jpg&amp;h=e73ade83&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<strong>享利</strong>，前啤梨晚報主持，因容貌曾被誤認為是黃洋達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。他與啤梨晚報主持相熟， 屬啤線人物。其人私怨到極點，比起黃毓民有過之而無不及，其論點與熱狗一樣，亦經常以「黃屍」批評黃絲。 關鍵時刻亦都會為黃毓民及啤梨辯護。 面容更與近期的選舉主任黃展翹撞樣：<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMGSR4qV.jpg&amp;h=1dbd470d&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以被懷疑一人分飾多角，投身政府DQ候選人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。但好彩其節目冇咩人睇無需要擔心。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"48d0ec0deb52e12c16dce3e332c58b7739d392db","tid":2138520,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T16:14:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed82bb9d7c90ff194fbd2b12773b92af92745f2e","tid":2138520,"uid":244082,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fbb5ddcb5c1212f436a5cd40bb67287b25608055","tid":2138520,"uid":196968,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"542e9d9f59bfc9042d1e74bc0e47db2688a56fab","tid":2138520,"uid":244082,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d912bb389ae2782ceb9df3f57d54b2f631f8af5a","tid":2138520,"uid":196968,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T15:48:37.000Z","msg":"碌左個橙入黎